reviewText:
This version is great, you get a laniard for your id's, a set of postcards, a faux finished picture frame (though it is cheaply made, but still nice looking) a pamphlet and of course the bonus DVD.

The concert is great, easily one of their bests. And the ending of the second DVD is very touching when they play Star[K]night. If you do not own this and are considering buy it, BUY IT ! You will not be disappointed.
